weatherman Flip Spiceland and sportscaster Jim Huber. All of the commentators 
except Ellerbee do other work for CNN. Among the network evening newscasts, 
only NBC still regularly airs commentary by John Chancellor. George Will 
comments for ABC News on an irregular basis. CBS discontinued commentaries 
after Bill Moyers, who delivered them, quit in 1986 and returned to public TV. 
