<P>
Claudio Abbado says his appointment this week as conductor of the Berlin 
Philharmonic will not interfere with his post as musical director of the Vienna 
State Opera. "I am profoundly honored. Naturally I accept the appointment but I 
won't leave Vienna," the 56-year-old Abbado said in an interview with the Rome 
