</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
REWARDS; AIRPLANE ACCIDENTS -- IOWA; ENGINES; GENERAL ELECTRIC CO 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA101389-0057 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 119933 </DOCID>
