<TEXT>
<P>
New York Yankee outfielder Dave Winfield has agreed to pay $163,000 in alimony 
and attorneys' fees to a woman that a jury in Houston ruled is his common-law 
wife. 
</P>
<P>
Winfield agreed to the payment and postponed his appeal of the jury's ruling in 
June that he and Sandra Renfro had a common-law marriage in 1982-85. 
</P>
