<P>
RIGHT TO LIFE LEAGUE OF SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA; ABORTION; RIGHT TO LIFE; WOMENS 
RIGHTS; COUNSELING; PREGNANCY; DIAGNOSTIC TESTS; CLINICS; MEDICAL MALPRACTICE; 
INJUNCTIONS; SUITS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
