<HEADLINE>
<P>
A WHO'S-WHO GUEST LIST OF THE RITZ-CARLTON 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Ritz-Carlton keeps a list of its big-name guests -- those who have agreed 
to be included, that is. Among them are: 
</P>
<P>
</P>
<P>
Alwaweed Bin Talal Bin Abdulaziz al Saud (Crown Prince of Saudi Arabia) 
</P>
